Modifications for MORPH/MORTAR (2026-06-09):
- Import paths rewritten: `stk.*` -> `morph.sparse.stk.*`.
- `backend/sputnik.py` renamed to `backend/autograd.py` (the file contains only
  torch.autograd.Function wrappers; the original sputnik CUDA backend was removed
  upstream in v0.0.5 — the name was a historical relic).
- triton_kernels.py: int16->int32 casts on all loaded block indices inside the
  Triton kernels (upstream unmerged PR #17 pattern). Fixes a Triton >=3.2
  dtype-promotion change that overflows int16 index arithmetic and causes illegal
  memory accesses for sparse dimensions > 32767 (int16 max * 128 blocking).
- Trimmed: eltwise_ops, random, tests (unused by MORTAR).
